# Task List: DirNav UI Component

- **Spec**: [spec.md](./spec.md)
- **Plan**: [plan.md](./plan.md)
- **Status**: Mostly implemented — remaining open items noted below.

> `[P]` = can run in parallel (no shared file dependency)
> Story tags: `[US1]`–`[US8]` map to spec.md user stories.

---

## Phase 1 – Setup ✅

- [x] T001 [P] Initialize SolidJS + TypeScript project with Vite build
- [x] T002 [P] Configure npm package (`package.json`, `main`, `exports` fields)
- [x] T003 [P] Add Playwright as test runner; create base test configuration
- [x] T004 [P] Define `DirectoryNode`, `DirectoryItem`, and state interfaces in `src/models/types.ts`

**Checkpoint**: Project builds; types compile; Playwright runs (even with no tests yet).

